{"tid":1878020,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"P牌換正式牌應該幾時申請","createTime":"2020-02-13T10:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T11:10:59.000Z","uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"805f1337a3a65759b188617bd2205d9509c1d7c9","tid":1878020,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T10:52:38.000Z","msg":"我個P牌下個月到期<br />\n1823網上咁寫：<br />\n&ldquo;持有暫准駕駛執照(電單車、機動三輛車、私家車或輕型貨車P牌)人士，必須在完成後暫准駕駛期後的3年內提出申請正式執照，否則，他必須重新報考駕駛考試及完成暫准駕駛期，方可再次申請。&rdquo;<br />\n即係我完左P牌先可以申請正式牌<br />\n定可以依家寄信去申請定先呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525d7d833059630a96fc1bb8b6ed02c6666f7351","tid":1878020,"uid":53481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T10:53:29.000Z","msg":"完左P牌先"},{"pid":"39ecd00ce10153eaadb16f8ace215339251cf0b9","tid":1878020,"uid":23011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T10:54:49.000Z","msg":"P牌到期後第一日可以開始申請，而P牌到期後三年內都唔申請就作廢要重考"},{"pid":"1ec6ed49136fab3756ec3770a48bed4bb559d8e0","tid":1878020,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:10:59.000Z","msg":"Thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}